I'm betting the rods are on wrong--how much do you want to bet he didn't do
the "drop test" on his rods (install the rod, torque it down, put a little
pad in the cylinder spigot right under the rod, pick up the little end and
let loose; it should drop freely) before he put the pistons and jugs on?
